{"content": "<p>I know almost nothing about music NFTs so asked on X...and boy MintFace got schooled. A list of artists mentioned is below or read the <a href=\"https://x.com/mintfaced/status/1868542058811797541\">original thread</a>.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t<h2>Stefanie Neal</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>A London born, Sydney based, self-taught mixed media artist who has been honing her creativity since childhood. Introduced to NFTs in October 2021. Her <a href=\"https://www.niftygateway.com/itemdetail/primary/0x673ef018a7287c223ebec6b39f3ab29323dc3b52/10/\">first music track 'Glitch'</a> sold 35 editions.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"249\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/stefanie-neal-1024x341.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/stefanie-neal-1024x341.jpeg 1024w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/stefanie-neal-300x100.jpeg 300w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/stefanie-neal-768x256.jpeg 768w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/stefanie-neal-600x200.jpeg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/stefanie-neal.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"My latest audiovisual is now live. Topics include Incels, furries, dipshits, politics and much more. \t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Stefanie Neal</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://app.manifold.xyz/c/sideways\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tMINT 'SIDEWAYS'\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t<h2>Violetta Zironi</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Violetta is holding the torch for the new chapter of the music industry. With her music NFTs, she rewards her holders with deeper access to her world, in a way that goes beyond just the music, creating a real synergy between herself and the receivers of her music. Her first NFT album <a href=\"https://market.violettazironi.com/1/collections/0x70be4e3761188d0a8c525e54bb81c4ea97712de4\">'Moonshot'</a> was released in April 2022.</p>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qJoD1g9bHLE\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"Collecting music, like art.\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Violetta Zironi</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://market.violettazironi.com/1/collections/0x70be4e3761188d0a8c525e54bb81c4ea97712de4\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tMINT 'A MOONSHOT'\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t<h2>\nMariana Makwaia</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p><a href=\"https://www.transient.xyz/mint/cherry-cvnt\" data-wplink-edit=\"true\">\"Cherry Cvnt\"</a> addresses the holistic nature of women contrasted with the superficiality of their image (in the media, society and AI). Madonna vs Whore Coquette vs Dominatrix Cherry vs Cvnt This song is about the female gaze and the freedom to embody dualities.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"249\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/makwaia-1024x341.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/makwaia-1024x341.jpeg 1024w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/makwaia-300x100.jpeg 300w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/makwaia-768x256.jpeg 768w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/makwaia-1320x440.jpeg 1320w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/makwaia-600x200.jpeg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/makwaia.jpeg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"My identity is subject to change.\" \t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Mariana Makwaia</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.transient.xyz/mint/cherry-cvnt\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tMINT 'A CHERRY CVNT'\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t<h2>Ed Balloon</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Artist, Musician, and creator of BSIOD and <a href=\"https://magiceden.io/collections/ethereum/0x9902037397c0909b440cbe5eed8e5eb84a2d7ba8\" data-wplink-edit=\"true\">Run ED Collection</a>. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"249\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/ed-balloon-1024x341.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/ed-balloon-1024x341.jpeg 1024w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/ed-balloon-300x100.jpeg 300w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/ed-balloon-768x256.jpeg 768w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/ed-balloon-600x200.jpeg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/ed-balloon.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"Let’s keep things flowing.\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Ed Balloon</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://magiceden.io/collections/ethereum/0x9902037397c0909b440cbe5eed8e5eb84a2d7ba8\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tMINT 'A RUN ED'\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t<h2>LATASHÁ</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p><strong>Latashá is an extraordinary visionary who defies categorization. As a multi-hyphenated entrepreneurial artist, she fearlessly traverses artistic boundaries, transcending genres and mediums to convey her powerful message and vibrational call. Known initially as an independent hip hop artist, Latashá's artistic range extends far beyond, encompassing dance, punk, and various other expressive forms.</strong></p>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LfoT7yAsvb8\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"infinite.\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>LATASHÁ</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://tash55.xyz/#1\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tMINT 'A TEN'\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t<h2>Produced by dav</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>CC0 maxi who gives away a ton of seed music. Based in Los Angeles. <a href=\"https://x.com/producedbydav/highlights\">Latest projects</a>.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"249\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/produced-by-sav-1024x341.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/produced-by-sav-1024x341.jpeg 1024w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/produced-by-sav-300x100.jpeg 300w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/produced-by-sav-768x256.jpeg 768w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/produced-by-sav-600x200.jpeg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/produced-by-sav.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"liquidity is a function of idea quality.\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>dav</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://zora.co/collect/base:0x131d9239a64521bb3b41d1d21e3d2b0419d029b8\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tMINT 'CYCLES'\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://theline.wtf/listing/david/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tListen on The Line 615\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t<h2>Rare Scrilla</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>In music for 20+ years and made first crypto themed record in 2014. Listen to latest <a href=\"https://foundation-media.ffm.to/42069\">RARE SCRILLA 42069</a>. ...or pick up a limited edition Bitcoin themed album from 2020. 100 copies created. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"516\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/soundmoney-1024x706.webp\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/soundmoney-1024x706.webp 1024w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/soundmoney-300x207.webp 300w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/soundmoney-768x530.webp 768w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/soundmoney-600x414.webp 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/soundmoney.webp 1290w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"Turn my memes up.\" \t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>RARE SCRILLA</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://rarescrilla.com/products/sound-money\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tGET 'Sound Money'\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t<h2>Dominos Music</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>DOMS is about more than expanding the PFP NFT space on Base + utility behind the <a dir=\"ltr\" role=\"link\" href=\"https://x.com/search?q=%24DOM&amp;src=cashtag_click\">$DOM</a> token... It is about telling the stories of the people who make DOMS special. <a href=\"https://x.com/doms4ever/status/1865111099529662859\">Watch the documentary</a> on DOM.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"675\" height=\"900\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/Domino.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/Domino.jpeg 675w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/Domino-225x300.jpeg 225w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/Domino-400x533.jpeg 400w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/Domino-600x800.jpeg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 675px) 100vw, 675px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"Just be yourself. Stick to your truth. Tell your story, endlessly. DOMS FOREVER\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Dominos Music</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://gallery.manifold.xyz/listing?listingId=6095\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tMINT 'SELF REFLECTING'\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t<h2>Pandelic</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Eric Pan builds multi-sensory playgrounds around music. Mixing piano, photography, art installation, and immersive storytelling, Eric invites audiences to engage with songs and improvisation through physical exploration.</p>https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=M96A8xVrpIQ\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"The Air Is Made Of Music.\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Pandelic</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://ericpan.bandcamp.com/merch/travel-poems-limited-edition-trilogy-boxset-all-3-cds-extras\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tGET 'TRAVEL POEMS'\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t<h2>Anonymous Nobody</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Minting since 1/25/20. </p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"319\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/anonymous-nobody-1024x436.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/anonymous-nobody-1024x436.jpeg 1024w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/anonymous-nobody-300x128.jpeg 300w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/anonymous-nobody-768x327.jpeg 768w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/anonymous-nobody-1536x653.jpeg 1536w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/anonymous-nobody-1320x561.jpeg 1320w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/anonymous-nobody-600x255.jpeg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/anonymous-nobody.jpeg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"We’re lucky to be around so many great artists of our time. You all are great people.Thanks for blessing me with your art over the last 5 years. I’ve been lucky enough to be amongst some of the greatest artists of our time. Imagine being a pioneer of a new medium of art.\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Anonymous Nobody</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.soundclick.com/kaspermartyrphantom\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tLISTEN NOBODY'S UNDERGROUND HIP-HOP (KASPER MARTYR PHANTOM 2005-2010)\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t<h2>More musicians in NFTS to follow:</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p><a href=\"https://x.com/songadaymann\">16 years a song a day</a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/agniis_eg\">Agniis </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/BlackDave\">Black Dave </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/matthewchaim\">Chaim</a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/dead_marcelo\">Dead Marcelo</a> <br /><a href=\"https://x.com/EmmyWalka\">Emmy Walker </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/_GLOWA_\">GLOWA </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/illaDaProducer\">Illa Da Producer </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/iineslobo\">Inê Lobo </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/ivaavimusic\">Ivaavi </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/0xKosmos_\">KOSMOS </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/LarkPopMusic\">Lark Music</a> <br /><a href=\"https://x.com/maisonclone\">Maison Clone </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/m0niqueRene\">M0nique Renee </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/Mshartistry\">Midday </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/MiRetratito\">Mi Retratito </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/NielsVen\">Neils Ven</a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/Nor44_lab\">Nor44 Lab</a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/ovachinsky\">OVA </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/perpetualdreamm\">Perpetual Dream </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/plutonicmind\">Plutonic Mind </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/PurzBeats\">Purz Beats </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/seedphrase\">Seedphrase </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/songcamp_\">Song Camp</a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/stvdionouveau\">Stvdio Nouveau</a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/TheMindOfSlyme\">The Mind of Slyme </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/UDntKnwWhoWeAre\">U Don't Know Who We are </a><br /><a href=\"https://x.com/vovabraxas\">Vov Abraxas </a></p>\t\t\n\t\t\t<h2>CoopahTrooper</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Coop Records has 100+ artists on <a href=\"http://cooprecords.xyz\">http://cooprecords.xyz</a>.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"503\" src=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/coop-1024x687.jpeg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/coop-1024x687.jpeg 1024w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/coop-300x201.jpeg 300w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/coop-768x515.jpeg 768w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/coop-1320x885.jpeg 1320w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/coop-600x402.jpeg 600w, https://digital-artist-economy.ghost.io/content/images/2024/12/coop.jpeg 1470w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"More recently we onboarded DJ Seinfeld, LP Giobbi and Vandelux. Disco Lines and Zeds coming this week too!\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Coop</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>"}